INSERT INTO `notes`
VALUES (913, NULL, 234, 732,
        '<p>The fact that banks are not fond of Bitcoin has been known for a long time. And it is hardly surprising!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On the one hand Bitcoin is a competition for banks, because it allows the transfer of value without intermediaries, and on the other hand it is the cause of capital flight from the banking system (e.g. bank deposits). Investing in Bitcoin and other cryptocurrencies gives much better opportunities to earn and higher rates of return.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Investing in cryptocurrencies is not against banking laws. In spite of this, sometimes you can hear news that someone&#39;s card/account was blocked just because he made a transfer of funds from a cryptocurrency exchange to his bank account or wanted to buy cryptocurrency using a payment card.</p>\r\n',
        '2021-02-10 17:12:03', '2021-02-10 17:12:03', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `notes`
VALUES (914, NULL, 234, 615,
        '<p>The risk/reward ratio is obtained by comparing the potential loss (in pips, in monetary units or percentages) with the potential profit. These values can be defined, for example, in Stop Loss and Take Profit orders. Although the use of the risk/reward ratio/ratio is quite natural and theoretically does not cause any problems to anyone, there are, however, several problematic issues. I would like to describe two that, in my opinion, most often concern traders with little experience on the market (but not only). The first one is purely formal and mainly related to communication. The second one is related to understanding the nature of risk and the relationship between average profits and losses and the percentage of profitable and losing trades.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Using the risk/reward relationship often creates problems in communication. The most common errors here are two. The first is when we say, for example, that we are using a risk-reward ratio of 5:1, thinking of a situation in which our potential profit is five times greater than the potential loss. A 5:1 ratio means that this risk is five times greater than the potential gain, and we most often make the mistake here of presenting a risk to gain ratio rather than a risk to gain ratio.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n',
        '2021-02-10 17:17:05', '2021-02-10 17:17:05', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `notes`
VALUES (915, NULL, 234, 588,
        '<p>In the simplest terms, it is a specially prepared computer program that analyzes data from the market faster than a human being, so as to be able to buy and sell a specific asset at the right time. Its purpose is to observe markets and react dynamically - according to a set of rules coded to it. However, automation alone cannot guarantee users profits - if it did, everyone would become a billionaire. In fact, making money with bots is not as easy as it is described - and traders who use them must have experience! Assuming that most people do not have this baggage, there is a high probability that they will fall into the trap of platforms offering easy money. However, it is important to realize that bots are only a tool that can improve trading and decision making speed, not a golden ticket to guaranteed income.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A bot can automate cryptocurrency trading, but here strategy is also important. Experienced traders, sharing their observations, more than once stressed that the &quot;set it and forget it&quot; rule does not work here. What is more, there are many types of bots and each of them is programmed for different purposes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Many traders say that the chances of making money using someone else&#39;s software are really low because someone who builds an effective bot will not be willing to share it with others.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To sum up, a beginner who has no idea how the market works will not be able to make much money in this field.</p>\r\n',
        '2021-02-10 17:21:10', '2021-02-10 17:21:10', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `notes`
VALUES (916, NULL, 234, 582,
        '<p>Vechain provides its users with the official VeChain Thor Wallet mobile wallet, available for both Android and iOS (Apple) devices. VeChain is also compatible with the popular multiwallet (supporting multiple cryptocurrencies) Trust Wallet, also available on Anrdoid and iOS. For desktop wallets, look out for Atomic Wallet, which is available for Windows, macOS, and Linux.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vechain is also supported by the most popular hardware wallet, Ledger Nano S, via the VeForge Vault app.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Note that as of July, the VeChain network is running on a standalone blockchain, which means that VET is not an ERC20 token, as was the case with VEN.</p>\r\n',
        '2021-02-10 17:23:29', '2021-02-10 17:23:29', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `notes`
VALUES (917, NULL, 239, 628,
        '<p>In my opinion, today the biggest real value behind bitcoin is its globally recognized brand. Bitcoin = cryptocurrency = blockchain. Most people in the world probably don&#39;t see the difference between bitcoin, which to them is the only recognizable cryptocurrency, and blockchain technology. A globally recognized brand alone can be worth a lot of money.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All of this makes it interesting for financial institutions and large corporations to use bitcoin as an alternative form of investment. They can make it into digital gold, which they will sell in bundles as intermediaries to various investors, while making money on speculation themselves. They can do this for profit, and the real value of bitcoin has little to do with it, as creating value out of thin air and selling every new piece of paper with the word &quot;security&quot; on it is standard today.</p>\r\n',
        '2021-02-10 17:26:06', '2021-02-10 17:26:06', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `notes`
VALUES (918, NULL, 239, 635,
        '<p>Leverage is used when investing in financial markets, mainly forex. It multiplies the capital invested. This allows investors who do not have much capital to invest effectively, also those who like riskier investments can implement that strategies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On such platforms you can usually choose the leverage for your account. In some countries you can find leverage even as high as 2000:1.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How does leverage work? It multiplies the available capital. For example, with a leverage of 30:1, each USD on your account has a purchasing power of 30 USD This means that by investing 10.000 USD you can make investments that would normally cost 300.000 USD.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In practice it looks like this:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The investor wants to open a Buy trade on the currency pair EURUSD in the size of 0.2 lot. The size of this contract is 20000 euros. If he did not use any leverage, he would have to invest this amount, in the case of a leverage of 1:10 the amount necessary for the investment is only 2000 euro, while in the case of a leverage of 1:30 it is only 667 euro. And if one uses a leverage of 1:100, then only 200 euros are needed to open such an investment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Assuming that the opening price was 1.0978 and the closing price was 1.11 then such an investment will yield a profit of about 222 euros, regardless of the leverage used. However, since in the case of a leverage of 1:10 the margin is equal to 2000 euro, the profit is about 10%, while in the case of a leverage of 1:30 the margin is equal to 668 euro, so here the profit is about 30%.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Due to the fact that the leverage allows opening larger positions with less capital, the profits can be higher. At the same time it should be remembered that it is a double-edged sword - not only profits but also losses are bigger.</p>\r\n',
        '2021-02-10 17:29:18', '2021-02-10 17:29:18', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `notes`
VALUES (919, NULL, 239, 604,
        '<p>Uniswap, a fully decentralised protocol that enables trading on hundreds of cryptocurrencies based on the Ethereum network has released its UNI token. According to information shared on the official blog, 60% of the UNI resource will be allocated to the Uniswap community as part of the Airdrop action, with a quarter of it (15% of the total supply) going to users of the protocol based on a snapshot of 1 September 2020. Every user who has ever executed a transaction within the Uniswap protocol and smart-contract is privileged to receive 400 UNI tokens, which are available for trading on Binance or KuCoin.com, among others</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>How to receive tokens from the Uniswap airdrop?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Visit the Uniswap app - https://app.uniswap.org/.<br />\r\nConnect your ETH wallet.<br />\r\nIf your wallet qualifies, a box will appear in the Uniswap app saying &quot;UNI has arrived&quot;.<br />\r\nClick on &quot;Claim your tokens&quot; to claim your tokens. Don&#39;t forget to set an appropriate gas limit due to the high commission prices on the Ethereum network.</p>\r\n',
        '2021-02-21 22:33:50', '2021-02-21 22:33:50', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `notes`
VALUES (920, NULL, 239, 743,
        '<p>1inch jest zdecentralizowanym agregatorem giełdowym, kt&oacute;ry pobiera płynność z r&oacute;żnych giełd i może rozdzielić pojedynczą transakcję handlową na wiele DEX-&oacute;w. Technologia inteligentnych kontrakt&oacute;w umożliwia użytkownikom optymalizację i dostosowanie swoich transakcji. Wraz z wydaniem tokena 1INCH i dodaniem puli płynności do platformy, możesz teraz dodać płynność do puli płynności 1inch i postawić tokeny LP, aby zarobić token 1INCH.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aby uczcić wprowadzenie tokena 1INCH, 1inch rozdał darmowe tokeny dla wczesnych użytkownik&oacute;w i dostawc&oacute;w płynności. Wszystkie portfele, kt&oacute;re weszły w interakcję z 1inch przed 24 grudnia (00:00 UTC) są uprawnione do otrzymania token&oacute;w, jeśli spełnią określone warunki. Dodatkowe nagrody otrzymają też dostawcy płynności . 1inch rzoda r&oacute;wnież dodatkową pulę 15.055.000 1INCH dla użytkownik&oacute;w Mooniswap i Uniswap, a także dla użytkownik&oacute;w portfeli Argent, Authereum, Gnosis i Pillar.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Airdrop 1: 90,000,000 1INCH dla wczesnych użytkownik&oacute;w</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Odwiedź stronę roszczeń 1inch.<br />\r\nPodłącz sw&oacute;j portfel ETH.<br />\r\nKliknij na fioletowy przycisk konia w prawym g&oacute;rnym rogu i kliknij na &quot;Claim&quot;.<br />\r\nJeśli się kwalifikujesz, to otrzymasz darmowe tokeny 1INCH.<br />\r\nWszystkie portfele, kt&oacute;re weszły w interakcję z 1inch przed 24 grudnia (00:00 UTC) i dokonały co najmniej jednej transakcji przed 15 września lub dokonały czterech transakcji lub dokonały transakcji o łącznej wartości $20 kwalifikują się do otrzymania nagr&oacute;d.<br />\r\nDostawcy płynności 1inch otrzymają r&oacute;wnież darmowe tokeny 1INCH w oparciu o program wydobywania płynności ogłoszony wcześniej tej jesieni.<br />\r\n.<br />\r\nAirdrop 2: 15,055,000 1INCH dla innych użytkownik&oacute;w AMM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Odwiedź stronę rozczeń 1inch.<br />\r\nPodłącz sw&oacute;j portfel ETH.<br />\r\nKliknij na fioletowy przycisk konia w prawym g&oacute;rnym rogu i kliknij na &quot;Claim&quot;.<br />\r\nJeśli jesteś uprawniony, a następnie zobaczysz &quot;Community Rewards Wave 2&quot; przycisk roszczenia.<br />\r\nKryteria kwalifikacyjne pozostają takie same jak w przypadku pierwszego airdropi. Wszystkie portfele, kt&oacute;re weszły w interakcję z 1inch przed 24 grudnia (00:00 UTC) i dokonały co najmniej jednej transakcji przed 15 września lub dokonały czterech transakcji lub dokonały transakcji o łącznej wartości 20$ kwalifikują się do otrzymania nagr&oacute;d.<br />\r\nPula 3.570.000 token&oacute;w 1INCH jest dostępna dla uczestnik&oacute;w drugiego programu wydobywczego płynności, 4.800.000 token&oacute;w 1INCH jest dostępnych dla użytkownik&oacute;w Mooniswap, 310.000 token&oacute;w 1INCH jest dostępnych dla użytkownik&oacute;w zleceń limit, a 375.000 token&oacute;w 1INCH jest dostępnych dla portfeli Argent, Authereum, Gnosis i Pillar.<br />\r\nOpr&oacute;cz powyższych puli, dodatkowa pula 6.000.000 1INCH jest dostępna dla użytkownik&oacute;w Uniswap, kt&oacute;rzy nigdy nie wymieniali token&oacute;w na 1inch i Mooniswap oraz mieli co najmniej 20 unikalnych dni handlowych i co najmniej 3 transakcje w 2021 roku.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n',
        '2021-02-21 22:37:32', '2021-02-21 22:37:32', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `notes`
VALUES (921, NULL, 239, 725,
        '<p>Musisz zapłacić za obliczenia, niezależnie od tego, czy Twoja transakcja się powiedzie, czy nie. Nawet jeśli się nie powiedzie, g&oacute;rnicy muszą zatwierdzić i wykonać Twoją transakcję (obliczyć) i dlatego musisz zapłacić za to obliczenie, tak jak zapłaciłbyś za udaną transakcję.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ether (ETH) jest paliwem dla tej sieci. Kiedy wysyłasz tokeny, wchodzisz w interakcję z kontraktem, wysyłasz ETH lub robisz cokolwiek innego na blockchainie, musisz zapłacić za to obliczenie. Płatność ta jest obliczana w gazie, a gaz jest wypłacany w ETH.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Całkowity koszt transakcji =Limit Gazu * Cena Gazu</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Zazwyczaj, jeśli ktoś m&oacute;wi po prostu &quot;gaz&quot;, to m&oacute;wi o &quot;limicie gazu&quot;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pomyśl o Limicie Gazu jak o ilości litr&oacute;w/galon&oacute;w/jednostek paliwa do samochodu.&nbsp;<br />\r\nW przypadku samochodu, jest to 2,5 USD (cena) za galon (jednostka).<br />\r\nW przypadku Ethereum, jest to 20 GWEI (cena) za gaz (jednostka).<br />\r\nAby napełnić sw&oacute;j &quot;bak&quot;, potrzeba...<br />\r\n10 galon&oacute;w po 2,50$ = 25$<br />\r\n21000 jednostek gazu po 20 GWEI = 0,00042 ETH.<br />\r\nW związku z tym całkowita opłata za TX wyniesie 0,00042 Ether.<br />\r\nWysyłanie token&oacute;w ksoztuje zazwyczaj od ~50000 gazu do ~100000 gazu, więc całkowita opłata za TX wzrasta do 0,001 ETH - 0,002 ETH.</p>\r\n',
        '2021-02-21 22:40:49', '2021-02-21 22:40:49', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `notes`
VALUES (922, NULL, 239, 263,
        '<p>Mobilne portfele są og&oacute;lnie bezpieczniejsze niż portfele windowsowe czy osxowe, ale musisz być ostrożny przestrzegając następujących zasad-</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pobierz sw&oacute;j portfel przez apple app store lub play store i upewnij się, że otrzymujesz oficjalną wersję</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nie pobieraj wielu aplikacji kryptowalutowych i uważaj, aby uniknąć sideloadingu niekt&oacute;rych aplikacji na androida</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Jeżeli będziesz miał 1k dolar&oacute;w na koncie rozważ kupno portfela sprzętowego np. trezor, ledger lub safepal.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Upewnij się, że zapisałeś 12/24 słowną frazę seed i przechowuj ją w bezpiecznym miejscu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Koniecznie zapisz informacje odzyskiwania. M&oacute;j telefon był uszkodzony i byłem w stanie odzyskać m&oacute;j portfel samourai na nowym telefonie. Zabezpiecz sw&oacute;j portfel i telefon za pomocą pinu. Używaj r&oacute;żnych kod&oacute;w PIN.&nbsp;</p>\r\n',
        '2021-02-21 22:44:23', '2021-02-21 22:44:23', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
