        '{\"message\":{\"content\":660,\"type_id\":2,\"title\":\"What is vanity adress?\",\"reason\":1,\"comment_id\":777,\"description\":\"<p>This is kind of an address where you can add your personalized words or letters to make it unique and customise for yourself. A vanity address can start with a string of letters and numbers that is publicly available or else can start with a customized set of letters and numbers. In order to create a Bitcoin vanity address you need a generator known as Bitcoin Vanitygens. You can find most popular generator <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/vante.me\\/#!\\/order\\/start\\\" style=\\\"text-decoration:none\\\">here<\\/a> and a full instruction video <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=BzrNqqY7OKQ&amp;feature=youtu.be\\\" style=\\\"text-decoration:none\\\">here<\\/a>.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\"}}',
